Citation.sAbstract: Liquid liquid equilibrium (LLE) data for the ternary system (methylcyclohexane benzene N-formylmorpholine) are reported under atmospheric pressure and at temperatures ranging from 293.15 to 333.15 K. Complete phase diagrams were obtained by determining solubility and tie-line data. The tie-line data were compared with the results predicted by the UNIQUAC and the NRTL methods. Distribution coefficients, separation factors and selectivity were evaluated for the immiscibility region.
Citation.sTitle: Liquid liquid equilibria of methylcyclohexane benzene N-formylmorpholine at several temperatures
